        <h2>
            掠夺之手的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4560754">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4560754/" class="title-link">扼住掠夺之手</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4560754"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3331595/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3331595-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3331595/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">higbye</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-02"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-02 21:05:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4560754_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  此书深入探讨了政府与社会、市场之间的关系。秉承了经济学一贯的观点，认为政府是一个理性组织，不是万能的仁慈的第三者，而是市场的参与者。这些观点虽然并不是新的，但是两名作者以深厚的经济学功底，严密的逻辑对扼住掠夺之手的分析还是发人深思的。 力荐！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4560754_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4560754_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










